{"tid":1439786,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連登文宣「多快好省」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-08-10T08:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T10:11:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca77cfc6e871f8ada1ce542bd1b4da554d0d3986","tid":1439786,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:25:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190810/20746148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190810%2F20746148&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s8wCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=014047a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190810%2F20746148&h=a2e85d91\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190810/20746148</a><br />\n<br />\n連登文宣「多快好省」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190810/large/1565341599_b468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190810%2Flarge%2F1565341599_b468.jpg&h=3a33a43a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不斷收到各界轉發或反送中小朋友們send來的文宣組圖文海報短片&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n科技發達腦筋靈活，「文宣」已不止於文字宣傳像大陸的洗腦八股，廣告、海報都五花八門，亦黑色幽默，即使反送中示威人士面對的是數千發催淚彈橡膠子彈海綿彈布袋彈&hellip;&hellip;殺傷力強的武器，他們奮勇抗爭，背後也有一批高手蒐集海量資訊，日以繼夜地操作文宣。<br />\n<br />\n連登仔的文宣，十分出色。圖象設計、長輩圖、網傳海報、口號文字&hellip;&hellip;在前線血汗淚中，白色恐怖威嚇中，為香港人深惡痛絕的政警黑勾結不公義制度，表達了沈默而有力的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n而且「多、快、好、省」──毛澤東周恩來翻生，也得讚賞今日年輕人「數量多、速度快、質量好、成本省」。<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙街坊和示威者捱催淚彈，馬上就出大仙戴防毒豬嘴人神共憤，快到呢！而深水埗反送中激光劍海報，更獲《星戰》天行者麥克咸美在Twitter讚好。七月盂蘭近了，還配合時節發揮創意&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n設計者來自五湖四海，隱身幕後，甚至素未謀面，但卧虎藏龍。他們不像掌權者心腸歹毒，千方百計目的在逼害、摧毀、分化、誣衊、報復，「人格」和「精神」出問題。連登仔不為名利，「文攻武衞」，這團結令人感動！  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n全天候監控 (左丁山)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n最壞的人 (李純恩)"},{"pid":"59165f778985e0e0cf78cfdf1833db7413ab4bc3","tid":1439786,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f132d2036d2fcefad3ea6b4d6f839af1db5b997b","tid":1439786,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:11:19.000Z","msg":"其實我唔係咁贊成用噴漆將D標語周圍噴<br />\n但呢D文宣就應該周圍貼,將連儂牆越做越大"}]}